<a id="clickme"><img class="imagetask" src="../media/btn_writingtask.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/></a>
<br/><br/><br/>

  <ol id="questionList">
  
  <li>How well do you know the person you are writing to?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t1">You have known them for a long time.</a></li>
  <li><a id="t2">You have been writing to them for a long time.</a></li>
  <li><a id="t3">You have only just met them.</a></li>
  <li><a id="t4">You have never met them.</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p> 
  
  <li>What style of letter should you write?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t5">formal</a></li>
  <li><a id="t6">informal</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p> 

  <li>What do you have to do in this letter?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t7">make arrangements</a></li>
  <li><a id="t8">provide information</a></li>
  <li><a id="t9">explain a situation</a></li>
  <li><a id="t10">request information</a></li>
  <li><a id="t11">offer advice</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p> 

  <li>How many points do you have to cover in this letter?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t12">one</a></li>
  <li><a id="t13">two</a></li>
  <li><a id="t14">three</a></li>
  <li><a id="t15">four</a></li>
  <li><a id="t16">five</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p> 

  <li>What personal information would it be appropriate to include in this letter?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t17">your nationality</a></li>
  <li><a id="t18">where you live</a></li>
  <li><a id="t19">some details about your family</a></li>
  <li><a id="t20">your life history</a></li>
  <li><a id="t21">what you do</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p> 

  <li>According to the writing task, what do you have to askthe person you are writing to?</li>
  <list class="answerList1">
  
  <li><a id="t22">how they spend their free time</a></li>
  <li><a id="t23">where they live</a></li>
  <li><a id="t24">what they look like</a></li>
  <li><a id="t25">what they do</a></li>
  <li><a id="t26">what their future plans are</a></li>
  </list>
  <p class="linespace"></p>  
  </ol>
</section>

<section id="writingtask1">
<p class="popuptext">You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>

<p class="popuptext"><b>Your English teacher has found a new penfriend for you.</b></p>

<p class="popuptext"><b>Write a letter to the penfriend and introduce yourself. Tell them what you like doing in your free time. Ask your penfriend to tell you about their hobbies and interests.</b></p>

<p class="popuptext">You should write at least 150 words.</p>

<p class="popuptext">You do NOT need to write your own address.</p>

<p class="popuptext">Begin your letter as follows: Dear ...</p>

</section>

<section id="tips">
<p class="popuptext"> Before you begin writing, you should make sure you've understood the task correctly and that you know exactly what is expected in your letter.</p>
</section>


